sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor WP as Wajib Pajak
    participant UI as Android UI
    participant VM as Search Object SPPT ViewModel
    participant Repo as SimpbbRepository
    participant API as PBB-Ku Internal API
    participant DB as SQLite atau PostgreSQL

    WP->>UI: Ketik NOP atau nama WP
    UI->>VM: updateQuery(query)
    VM->>VM: Debounce dan validasi minimal karakter
    VM->>Repo: searchObjekPajak(query, limit)
    Repo->>API: POST objekPajak search dengan wrapper json
    API->>DB: Query tax_objects + tax_subjects
    DB-->>API: Daftar objek pajak
    API-->>Repo: Response wrapper json berisi daftar
    Repo-->>VM: Domain ObjekPajakSummary
    VM-->>UI: State sukses hasil pencarian
    UI-->>WP: Tampilkan daftar NOP

    WP->>UI: Pilih NOP
    UI->>VM: loadDetail(nop)
    VM->>Repo: getObjekPajakByNop(nop)
    Repo->>API: POST objekPajak getByNop dengan wrapper json
    API->>DB: Query detail objek dan subjek pajak
    DB-->>API: Detail objek pajak
    API-->>Repo: Response wrapper json berisi detail
    Repo-->>VM: Domain ObjekPajakDetail
    VM-->>UI: State detail sukses
    UI-->>WP: Tampilkan detail objek

    WP->>UI: Buka Histori SPPT atau Tunggakan
    UI->>VM: loadTaxBills(nop)
    VM->>Repo: listSpptByNop atau getTunggakan
    Repo->>API: POST sppt listByNop atau objekPajak getTunggakan
    API->>DB: Query sppt
    DB-->>API: Rows SPPT
    API-->>Repo: Response wrapper json berisi tagihan
    Repo-->>VM: Domain TaxBill
    VM-->>UI: State tagihan sukses
    UI-->>WP: Tampilkan status, nominal, jatuh tempo
